high_descs: Turn to the left and locate the chair in the corner.
Pick up the credit card from the seat of the chair.
Carry the credit card and turn left, then left again to find the coffee table.
Place the credit card on the plate on the left side of the table.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Hold the plate and turn to the left and then right to go back to the wall.
Place the plate on the floor bench along the wall.
anns.task_desc: Move a credit card and plate to a bench.

high_descs: Go to the chair to the left of the picture.
Pick up the credit card in the chair.
Take the card to the coffee table.
Put the card on the plate in front of the paper on the coffee table.
Pick up the plate with the card on it.
Go to the left around the table and across the room past the picture on the left to the shelf.
Set the plate down on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Set a plate with a credit card on it onto the shelf with the statue.

high_descs: Turn around and go over to the black chair.
Look at the seat cushion and pick up the blue credit card.
Turn left, go to stand between the couch and the coffee table, then turn left to face the coffee table.
Put the blue credit card down on the plate.
Pick up the plate with the credit card on it.
Turn left and head back the way you came, then turn right and go to the black shelf.
Put the plate on the shelf in front of the blue bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a credit card on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn to the left and go to the chair
pick up the credit card on the chair
Turn left and go to the glass coffee table
set the credit card down on the plate on the coffee table
Pick up the plate on the coffee table
Turn left, go to the wall, then turn right
Place plate on the bench
anns.task_desc: Put the credit card on a plate on a bench

high_descs: Walk towards the painting, turn left, and walk towards the sofa chair.
Pick up the credit card on the chair.
Turn left, walk towards the coffee table, and turn left to face the newspaper on the table.
Place the credit card on the plate.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Turn left, walk towards the sofa chair, hang right towards the trophy.
Place the plate in front of the blue circle.
anns.task_desc: Place the credit card on the plate to place it in front of the trophy.

high_descs: Turn left, go in front of the black chair.
Pick up the credit card from the chair cushion.
Turn left, walk to the side of the coffee table and face the coffee table.
Put the credit card on the white plate on the coffee table.
Pick up the plate with the credit card on it.
Turn left, walk towards the black chair, then turn right and walk towards the black platform.
Put the plate on the platform in front of the blue object.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a credit card on a black platform.
